To GL: so you can pick up powers from villagers/coven to give you a check/stalk/kill power, BUT you can also consume some of the dead UD players if necessary to get their powers.  For instance, if the VD goes down and you consume their power, you become the VD.  Or if the Necro goes down, same thing - you can consume them and become a Necro.  Consuming the powers turns the UD in the GY into a powerless UD Wight though.  However if you can construct it right, you can get the OGNecro to revive someone into another avatar, then later on if the OGNecro dies, you can Ghoul-consume their power to become a Necro yourself and therefore get a second Necro in the game.
